OL,3,CCheapest long-haul winter sun
OL,4,Cdestinations for UK travellers revealed
OL,6,FUK holidaymakers planning long-haul
OL,7,Fwinter sun holidays will pay less for
OL,8,Ftourist items in two out of three
OL,9,Fpopular destinations compared with a
OL,10,Fyear ago, new figures show.
OL,12,FAsian destinations offer the best
OL,13,Fbargains, occupying seven of the top
OL,14,F10 cheapest locations analysed for a
OL,15,Freport by Post Office Travel Money.
OL,17,FVietnam's Hoi An was found to have the
OL,18,Flowest local prices for UK visitors
OL,19,Fout of 30 destinations analysed.
