OL,6,FThe goods analysed include a cup of
OL,7,Ffilter coffee in a cafe or bar, a
OL,8,Fsmall bottle or tube of insect
OL,9,Frepellent, and a three-course evening
OL,10,Fmeal for two adults with a bottle of
OL,11,Fhouse wine.
OL,13,FLocal prices in third-placed Bali,
OL,14,FIndonesia, have risen by 10.8% since
OL,15,Flast autumn, but an 11.3% fall in the
OL,16,Fvalue of its currency ` the rupiah `
OL,17,Fagainst the pound means costs have
OL,18,Fdropped by 0.5% for visitors from the
OL,19,FUK.
